ng-include=\"'partials/doctor_request_info.html'\" class=\"\"><div class=\"nugg-overlay ng-hide\" ng-show=\"doctorRequestInfo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><ion-scroll direction=\"y\" class=\"content scroll-view ionic-scroll\"><div class=\"scroll\"><h3>Cannabis Evaluations</h3><p>Nugg is the easiest way to schedule your cannabis evaluation. Simply provide your availability and some basic contact information, and a patient support specialist will find an appointment for you with a licensed physician in your area.</p><p>We’ll send you a confirmation email within 24 hours with a few appointment times to choose from, pricing, and other info. Then confirm your appointment time, and you’re all set!</p><h4>How does a cannabis evaluation work?</h4><p>Consultations are private, discreet, and take about 20 minutes. The doctor will administer a basic exam, check vital signs, discuss your medical history and any other information you provide, then determine if a medicinal marijuana recommendation is right for you.</p><h4>What should I bring to my appointment?</h4><p></p><ul><li>- Valid California ID/Driver’s license or proof of residency.</li><li>- Any medical records/prescription medications you may have that pertain to your condition.</li><li>- Any prior medical marijuana recommendations.</li></ul><p></p><h4>Is this information accessible to government agencies or my employer?</h4><p>No. Our partner physicians follow strict HIPAA guidelines to ensure that all patient records are kept in the strictest confidentiality and shared only with dispensaries you order from (for patient verification purposes).</p><h4>What happens after my evaluation?</h4><p>Once you complete your evaluation, upload your new doctor’s recommendation in the “Account” tab, and we'll send you a <b>$10</b> credit toward your first order on Nugg!</p></div><div class=\"scroll-bar scroll-bar-v\"><div class=\"scroll-bar-indicator scroll-bar-fade-out\"></div></div></ion-scroll><div class=\"close\"><i class=\"close ion-ios-close-empty\" ng-click=\"$parent.doctorRequestInfo = false\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"></i></div></div></div><!-- ngInclude: 'partials/how_it_works.html' --><div ng-include=\"'partials/how_it_works.html'\" class=\"\"><div class=\"nugg-overlay ng-hide\" ng-show=\"howItWorks\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><ion-scroll direction=\"y\" class=\"content scroll-view ionic-scroll\"><div class=\"scroll\"><h3>How it Works</h3><h4>Browse cannabis products from reliable local dispensaries</h4><ul><li>Sativa, indica, and hybrid strains</li><li>Edibles</li><li>Concentrates</li><li>Tinctures, and more.</li></ul><h4>Get verified instantly</h4><ul><li>Safe &amp;
